title: How to Shape an Afro Fade | AXE | Instagroom
description:
This is Afro Fade à la Leroy. Crazy but contained. 

THE TOOLS:
AXE Natural Look Softening Cream
Hair pick
Curl sponge

THE STEPS:
1. Pick hair
2. Rub cream into palms
3. Squeeze into hair
4. Sponge for curls
